data.description: Bring all offers! This 4,800sf 3-level custom cabin rests on 5 acres on a quiet cul-de-sac with year-round well-maintained roads. Bring your horses, too, the horse corrals have spring water! Amazing mountain views from the huge picture windows gazing upon mountains and the San Luis Valley. 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a large basement rec room, 3 decks, and an over-sized RV garage... with an apartment above! Apartment would be perfect income property for Air BnB or VRBO.  Two offices, a loft library, and horse corrals! Ceiling fans and skylights have auto-closing feature to provide natural cooling and circulation. Custom cabinetry throughout. Brazilian granite countertops, and kitchen appliances are only 3-yrs old. Cameras with night vision and motion sensors offer security, with an app you can easily download and monitor/record. Only 10 minutes to Fort Garland, 5 minutes to Mountain Home Reservoir for fishing and boating. Home comes partially furnished. List of inclusions and exclusions to be provided. A perfect home for your family and friends, immaculate and ready to move into!
